вҖӘ-I don'tвҖҰ I don't know what--
вҖӘ-Come here. Come here.

397
00:18:57.666 --> 00:19:00.041
вҖӘ-I said come here.
вҖӘ-And then? What's going on here?

398
00:19:00.125 --> 00:19:02.583
вҖӘThis is not mine. Grandma. I swear.

399
00:19:02.666 --> 00:19:05.291
вҖӘDo you want to be
вҖӘa teenage mother like your mother was?

400
00:19:05.375 --> 00:19:07.166
вҖӘNo. I'm still a virgin. Gran.

401
00:19:07.250 --> 00:19:09.291
вҖӘOh. stop it. Mom. Wow.

402
00:19:09.375 --> 00:19:10.875
вҖӘShe said that it's not hers.

403
00:19:11.458 --> 00:19:12.958
вҖӘDon't tell me you believe her. Joyce.

404
00:19:14.708 --> 00:19:15.708
вҖӘSo. what's this?

405
00:19:15.791 --> 00:19:17.541
вҖӘMom. a word. please?

406
00:19:18.291 --> 00:19:19.541
вҖӘ[huffs]

407
00:19:25.291 --> 00:19:26.583
вҖӘIt's mine.

408
00:19:26.666 --> 00:19:28.333
вҖӘ-What?
вҖӘ-Yes.

409
00:19:29.250 --> 00:19:30.875
вҖӘI had a pregnancy scare.

410
00:19:30.958 --> 00:19:32.333
вҖӘWhat? At your age?

411
00:19:32.416 --> 00:19:35.166
вҖӘOh. Mom. give me a break. please.

412
00:19:35.250 --> 00:19:39.833
вҖӘ[sighs] But listen. I'm going to make sure
вҖӘthat this never happens to me again.

413
00:19:39.916 --> 00:19:40.916
вҖӘEver!

414
00:19:41.791 --> 00:19:43.583
вҖӘI've decided to getвҖҰ [sighs]

415
00:19:44.166 --> 00:19:46.166
<i>вҖӘвҖҰsterilised and tie my tubes.</i>

416
00:19:46.250 --> 00:19:48.458
вҖӘ-[Grace] <i>вҖӘWill Jonasi agree to that?</i>
вҖӘ-[Joyce] <i>вҖӘHe'll never allow it.</i>

417
00:19:48.541 --> 00:19:50.125
<i>вҖӘThat's why I didn't tell him.</i>

418
00:19:52.791 --> 00:19:53.916
вҖӘ[exhales sharply]

419
00:20:11.666 --> 00:20:13.416
вҖӘ[Joyce] <i>вҖӘ"Love is not proud.</i>

420
00:20:13.958 --> 00:20:17.000
<i>вҖӘIt doesn't dishonour others.</i>

421
00:20:17.958 --> 00:20:19.708
<i>вҖӘIt is not self-seeking."</i>

422
00:20:19.791 --> 00:20:22.541
вҖӘ-Is Mlungisi Gomora in transit?
вҖӘ-[laughing]

423
00:20:32.416 --> 00:20:34.583
вҖӘ[chattering]

424
00:20:42.125 --> 00:20:44.458
вҖӘ-Sister. How are you?
вҖӘ-Hello. how are you?

425
00:20:44.541 --> 00:20:45.750
вҖӘ-I'm good.
вҖӘ-It's been a while.

426
00:20:45.833 --> 00:20:46.833
вҖӘ-[nurse] Yes. it has.
вҖӘ-Oh. my word.

427
00:20:46.916 --> 00:20:49.083
вҖӘ[Jonasi] So you still work here? Huh?

428
00:20:49.166 --> 00:20:50.416
вҖӘ-How is everyone at home?
вҖӘ-[nurse] They're good.

429
00:20:50.500 --> 00:20:52.666
вҖӘ[Jonasi] Ah. that's good. [chuckles]

430
00:20:52.750 --> 00:20:54.416
вҖӘ-[elevator bell dings]
вҖӘ-[exhales sharply]

431
00:20:56.750 --> 00:20:58.250
вҖӘ-[whispers] Joyce.
вҖӘ-Hmm?

432
00:20:58.875 --> 00:21:00.291
вҖӘThank God you're done.

433
00:21:00.375 --> 00:21:01.375
вҖӘI didn't go through with it.

434
00:21:01.458 --> 00:21:04.375
вҖӘI couldn't do such a serious surgery
вҖӘbehind my husband's back.

435
00:21:04.458 --> 00:21:06.375
вҖӘSuch a serious thing
вҖӘwithout his knowledge.

436
00:21:06.458 --> 00:21:07.833
вҖӘHe's here.

437
00:21:08.416 --> 00:21:11.708
вҖӘ-Who's here?
вҖӘ-Jonasi. I just saw him right now.

438
00:21:11.791 --> 00:21:13.625
вҖӘ-No way. You're lying!
вҖӘ-I'm telling you. Joyce.

439
00:21:13.708 --> 00:21:15.500
вҖӘMom! How did he find out about this?

440
00:21:15.583 --> 00:21:17.333
вҖӘ-[door opens]
вҖӘ-[exclaims]

441
00:21:20.083 --> 00:21:21.250
вҖӘAll right then.

442
00:21:21.333 --> 00:21:24.125
вҖӘI'm sure you're ready for your procedure?

443
00:21:24.208 --> 00:21:26.500
вҖӘUh. Doctor. listen.

444
00:21:26.583 --> 00:21:28.958
вҖӘAs you can see. I'm already dressed.

445
00:21:29.041 --> 00:21:31.125
вҖӘI've decided not to go through
вҖӘwith this procedure.

446
00:21:31.208 --> 00:21:33.666
вҖӘ[doctor] I understand.
вҖӘit's a very big decision to make.

447
00:21:33.750 --> 00:21:37.083
вҖӘYou'll have to sign some papers
вҖӘfor the theatre cancellation.

448
00:21:37.166 --> 00:21:38.625
вҖӘIt'sвҖҰ It's fine. It's fine.

449
00:21:38.708 --> 00:21:41.833
вҖӘThe Gomora women
вҖӘhave kept the ward quite busy today.

450
00:21:41.916 --> 00:21:44.208
вҖӘEveryone here has got their hands full.

451
00:21:44.958 --> 00:21:46.541
вҖӘThe Gomora women?

452
00:21:46.625 --> 00:21:50.375
вҖӘAs we speak. there's another Gomora lady
вҖӘwho just gave birth down the passage.

453
00:21:51.083 --> 00:21:53.291
вҖӘIt is busy. It's very busy right now.

454
00:21:53.375 --> 00:21:58.000
вҖӘThat's why I said the Gomora women
вҖӘhave made this ward very busy today.

455
00:21:58.791 --> 00:22:00.666
вҖӘThere's another here as well.

456
00:22:02.708 --> 00:22:03.833
вҖӘ[gasps]

457
00:22:06.625 --> 00:22:09.041
вҖӘ[doctor] <i>вҖӘThe Gomora women</i>
<i>вҖӘare keeping us busy today.</i>

458
00:22:09.708 --> 00:22:11.125
вҖӘ[Joyce] <i>вҖӘThe Gomora women?</i>

459
00:22:11.750 --> 00:22:14.500
вҖӘ[doctor] <i>вҖӘThey have kept the ward</i>
<i>вҖӘquite busy today.</i>

460
00:22:14.583 --> 00:22:15.875
вҖӘ[Grace] Joyce.

461
00:22:15.958 --> 00:22:17.625
вҖӘJoyce. wait. Joyce.

462
00:22:17.708 --> 00:22:20.416
вҖӘ[doctor] <i>вҖӘAs we speak. there's another</i>
<i>вҖӘGomora lady down the passage.</i>

463
00:22:20.500 --> 00:22:23.208
вҖӘJoyce. Joyce! Wait.

464
00:22:23.291 --> 00:22:24.625
вҖӘ[baby coos]

465
00:22:24.708 --> 00:22:26.333
вҖӘ[Jonasi] I'm luckiest man in the world.

466
00:22:26.916 --> 00:22:28.875
вҖӘToday. you've made me a man amongst men.

467
00:22:28.958 --> 00:22:29.958
вҖӘ[chuckles]

468
00:22:36.916 --> 00:22:39.458
вҖӘ-[Jonasi shushing]
вҖӘ-[baby cooing]

469
00:22:41.375 --> 00:22:42.375
вҖӘJoyce.

470
00:22:42.458 --> 00:22:43.458
вҖӘ[Jonasi] Hmm?

471
00:22:53.250 --> 00:22:54.250
вҖӘJoyce.

472
00:23:05.166 --> 00:23:06.750
вҖӘ-[gasps]
вҖӘ-Joyce.
